<main>
    <section class="hero-title">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-cc-primary fw-bold">Our Mission: Compassion, Quality, Innovation</h1>
        <p class="lead">Discover the ClinicCare difference and our commitment to your health journey.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-7 mb-4">
                <h3 class="text-cc-primary mb-3">Who We Are</h3>
                <p>ClinicCare Health Center was founded in 2015 with a simple goal: to make high-quality healthcare accessible, efficient, and compassionate. We believe that technology should support, not hinder, the patient experience, which led to the creation of our integrated Queue & Appointments System.</p>
                <p>We are a dedicated team of general practitioners and specialists committed to serving the local community with integrity and expertise.</p>
                
                <h3 class="text-cc-primary mt-5 mb-3">Our Core Values</h3>
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> **Excellence:** Delivering the highest standards of medical care.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> **Empathy:** Treating every patient with respect and understanding.</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success me-2"></i> **Efficiency:** Utilizing modern systems to reduce wait times and streamline processes.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-lg-5 mb-4">
                <div class="card cc-card-public shadow p-4 bg-cc-light-blue h-100">
                    <h4 class="text-cc-primary">Why Choose ClinicCare?</h4>
                    <p>We combine personalized care with cutting-edge digital tools to offer a seamless healthcare experience.</p>
                    <a href="doctors-public.html" class="btn btn-cc-primary w-100 mb-3"><i class="fas fa-user-md me-2"></i> Meet Our Professionals</a>
                    <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-outline-success w-100"><i class="fas fa-location-arrow me-2"></i> Find Our Location</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
